  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/ebb68521c54978b8ef5632b6842ad8d7.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/ebb68521c54978b8ef5632b6842ad8d7.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/a160a86879e81ad565cd967a2f400a44.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/556ac53385b21a5147409437fb70e185.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/556ac53385b21a5147409437fb70e185.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/556ac53385b21a5147409437fb70e185.mp4?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy as many shapes as you can within the given time. Some shapes may shoot projectiles upon destruction, sparking chaotic chain reactions. Break enough shapes, and you might even level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/1b3d25facfbf4be33b392e77887b1791.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/9ce631e59b7a206a6bdcd81fd1f1689f.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/9ce631e59b7a206a6bdcd81fd1f1689f.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/9ce631e59b7a206a6bdcd81fd1f1689f.mp4?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every destroyed shape drops shards - how convenient! Gather as many as possible because shards are the key to your progress as the game’s currency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/f51209b2420e29a8cb156b5e00e9034d.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/939fc5e2e34177ac3909cd2fe2cc9aa8.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/939fc5e2e34177ac3909cd2fe2cc9aa8.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/939fc5e2e34177ac3909cd2fe2cc9aa8.mp4?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your shards to purchase a variety of upgrades from the shop. Empower Max Manos and unlock new abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/534e717d9cbcc9ddc81f118a99065454.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/8836f424aef3007b3707a1616954a306.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/8836f424aef3007b3707a1616954a306.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/8836f424aef3007b3707a1616954a306.mp4?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Max Manos upgraded, you’ll destroy shapes more efficiently, collect even more shards, and buy even better upgrades. It's a circle of life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/bcf51b7a38c90761e30262e31596f659.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/2d45fba0e25b00c59e2a86f85949b350.poster.avif?t=1758546702\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/2d45fba0e25b00c59e2a86f85949b350.webm?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428620/extras/2d45fba0e25b00c59e2a86f85949b350.mp4?t=1758546702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now that Max Manos is an unstoppable force, let chaos reign supreme across the screen.</p>",
